==English==
===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Αncient Greek]] '''[[καρδιακός]]''' (''kardiakos'') "relating to the heart", from '''[[καρδία]]''' (''kardia'') "heart".

===Adjective===
'''cardiac'''
# Pertaining to the [[heart]].

